OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FApple staff make bid for   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffirst union at a US store  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Workers at Apple's Grand Central       
OL,6, Station store in New York have         
OL,7, announced a plan to start a union.     
OL,9,FIf their bid is successful it would be 
OL,10,Fthe first union at one of the tech     
OL,11,Fgiant's US stores.                     
OL,13,FThe group of staff known as Fruit Stand
OL,14,FWorkers United must get signatures of  
OL,15,Fsupport from 30% of colleagues at the  
OL,16,Fstore to qualify for a union election. 
OL,18,FThe move follows unionisation drives by
OL,19,Fstaff at Starbucks and Amazon. Apple   
OL,20,Fhas not commented on the announcement. 
